Introduction

E11iVYN (read as Eleven), is a South Korean pre-debut girl group under MOAI Entertainment. The group was first introduced on December 23, 2024, as IWU. In late January 2025, the group rebranded to its current name. The group consists of Chaerin, Juha, Youngeun and Shion. On March 19, 2025 E11iVyn posted a version of their lineup reveal where Lu Yuting has been edited out, suggesting her departure from the group. On March 18, 2025 Yuting confirmed that she will not be debuting with the group. They are set to debut in May 2025.
